WEBVTT

01:41.600 --> 01:47.240
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:50.000 --> 01:51.920
THREE DAYS LATER

01:52.000 --> 01:53.920
YONG'AN GATE

02:00.840 --> 02:02.160
JINGQUE HOUSE

02:02.240 --> 02:03.160
So many people today.

02:03.240 --> 02:04.520
It is quite a spectacle.

02:04.600 --> 02:05.440
It really is.

02:07.040 --> 02:09.080
Changyu, you practically can't stay away

02:09.160 --> 02:10.639
from the Marquis for a single day.

02:10.720 --> 02:12.320
Did you have to come join the crowd?

02:12.920 --> 02:14.400
When I came to the capital,
he was there for me.

02:14.920 --> 02:16.400
Now that he returns in triumph,

02:16.480 --> 02:17.680
of course I'm here.

02:20.960 --> 02:23.080
Song Yan of the Ministry of Rites
Internal Affairs Office

02:23.160 --> 02:25.360
was appointed to oversee
matters of ritual instruction.

02:25.440 --> 02:27.320
Yet he has proved incompetent in office

02:27.400 --> 02:29.080
and failed in his duties.

02:29.160 --> 02:30.360
He is stripped of his post,

02:30.440 --> 02:31.880
sent back to his native place,

02:31.960 --> 02:33.080
and barred from future service.

02:36.560 --> 02:37.840
-We have waited so long.
-There he is!

02:37.920 --> 02:39.080
-He is here!
-He is here!

02:39.160 --> 02:40.360
YONG'AN GATE

02:43.840 --> 02:45.080
He is here! Changyu, look!

02:46.280 --> 02:47.560
There he is!

02:47.640 --> 02:49.040
Marquis Wu'an!

03:04.960 --> 03:07.760
MARQUIS WU'AN

03:38.080 --> 03:39.160
You are not coming?

03:40.960 --> 03:42.720
What is there to see? I'm good.

03:45.640 --> 03:47.920
-Marquis Wu'an!
-Marquis Wu'an!

03:49.400 --> 03:50.920
Look over here, Marquis!

03:51.440 --> 03:53.920
-Marquis Wu'an!
-Marquis Wu'an!

03:54.000 --> 03:56.800
-Look this way!
-Marquis Wu'an!

03:57.320 --> 03:58.560
Marquis Wu'an!

03:58.640 --> 04:00.400
Look over here, Marquis!

04:02.960 --> 04:05.000
XIE

04:40.640 --> 04:41.480
Halt.

04:42.520 --> 04:43.680
Look over here!

04:44.280 --> 04:45.320
Changyu,

04:45.400 --> 04:47.320
why do you not throw something too?

04:48.520 --> 04:49.440
I did not bring anything.

04:49.520 --> 04:50.600
Just toss something!

04:50.680 --> 04:52.280
Does anyone have a handkerchief?

04:52.880 --> 04:54.600
-Anyone got a handkerchief?
-Anyone bring one?

04:55.120 --> 04:56.400
What is the fun in that?

04:57.520 --> 04:59.520
Come on. Let me show you how it is done.

05:05.520 --> 05:07.400
Watch me knock him out.

05:09.440 --> 05:11.280
What are you doing?

05:11.360 --> 05:13.240
-I…
-You what?

05:13.320 --> 05:15.560
GUO'S TAVERN

05:16.160 --> 05:18.200
Marquis Wu'an!

05:18.280 --> 05:19.320
Marquis Wu'an!

05:19.400 --> 05:20.720
Marquis Wu'an!

05:57.600 --> 05:59.560
Whose ribbon was that?

06:00.560 --> 06:02.760
Could it be Marquis Wu'an
already has someone he likes?

06:07.400 --> 06:09.200
So many girls threw handkerchiefs
along the road,

06:09.280 --> 06:10.520
yet the Marquis paid them no heed.

06:10.600 --> 06:13.160
Which family's young lady could that be?

06:15.880 --> 06:17.880
Is that not the Flower-Adorned General?

06:17.960 --> 06:19.280
It really is General Fan.

06:20.960 --> 06:22.640
Look!

06:22.720 --> 06:23.760
Over here!

06:23.840 --> 06:24.880
Over here!

06:29.200 --> 06:31.800
Our General Fan is every bit
as formidable as any man.

06:31.880 --> 06:33.840
No wonder the Marquis favors her.

06:33.920 --> 06:35.880
-What is so impressive about that?
-Our Marquis

06:35.960 --> 06:37.880
-is a man of war, not petty romance.
-Exactly.

06:37.960 --> 06:40.520
That pig butcher of yours
is not worthy of him at all.

06:40.600 --> 06:41.520
Not worthy!

06:41.600 --> 06:43.640
Our Flower-Adorned General
has fought countless battles,

06:43.720 --> 06:45.520
captured Prince Changxin,
and earned great merit.

06:45.600 --> 06:47.720
She wouldn't stoop to marry your Marquis.

06:47.800 --> 06:49.400
Stop flattering yourselves.

06:49.480 --> 06:51.520
-Exactly.
-Stop flattering yourselves.

06:51.600 --> 06:53.360
Our Marquis is a hero among men.

06:53.440 --> 06:55.680
He would never lower himself
for a mere pig butcher.

06:55.760 --> 06:57.200
Exactly. She's a pig butcher.

06:57.280 --> 06:59.600
-What's there to brag about?
-Her achievements speak for themselves.

06:59.680 --> 07:01.240
She'd never marry
a rough soldier like him.

07:01.320 --> 07:02.960
-He's not some rough soldier!
-Watch your words!

07:05.080 --> 07:06.520
Stop arguing already.

07:06.600 --> 07:09.240
We just want to watch a good romance
unfold between a hero and a beauty.

07:09.320 --> 07:10.760
Can you all stop shouting?

07:10.840 --> 07:12.040
Exactly.

07:13.440 --> 07:14.920
-Look at that.
-Exactly.

07:18.000 --> 07:19.840
-Marquis Wu'an!
-Look at me!

07:22.000 --> 07:23.000
Look this way!

07:23.080 --> 07:26.240
XIE

07:34.720 --> 07:37.120
-Marquis Wu'an!
-Marquis Wu'an!

07:37.640 --> 07:38.880
Marquis Wu'an!

07:38.960 --> 07:40.200
Marquis Wu'an!

07:49.040 --> 07:51.960
TAVERN

08:00.120 --> 08:01.880
Heaven is unjust.

08:12.400 --> 08:17.160
XIE FAMILY MAUSOLEUM

08:17.240 --> 08:20.480
HONOR THE ANCESTORS, UNITE THE CLAN

09:05.520 --> 09:07.360
When a man grows old,

09:08.800 --> 09:10.160
his memory starts to fail.

09:10.800 --> 09:11.720
Today,

09:12.240 --> 09:15.120
I even forgot to bring
your favorite osmanthus cakes.

09:33.680 --> 09:35.400
You come here every year on this day.

09:36.080 --> 09:38.160
What is it? Are my parents

09:38.240 --> 09:39.480
too peaceful down there,

09:40.440 --> 09:42.360
so you come to stir
their anger once a year?

09:46.160 --> 09:48.480
You have been hiding for several days.

09:49.040 --> 09:51.040
At last, you show yourself.

09:56.600 --> 09:59.640
Today is your mother's death anniversary.

10:00.240 --> 10:02.960
Let the fighting and killing
wait for another day.

10:12.680 --> 10:14.440
No matter how serious the matter,

10:14.960 --> 10:18.560
it can wait until we paid respects
to your parents.

10:19.960 --> 10:20.840
Come.

10:38.960 --> 10:43.120
‎HONOR THE ANCESTORS, UNITE THE CLAN

10:46.720 --> 10:50.360
SPIRIT TABLET OF THE LATE LORD XIE LINSHAN
SPIRIT TABLET OF HIS WIFE, LADY WAN

11:36.040 --> 11:37.800
Chancellor, you dismissed your guards.

11:38.840 --> 11:40.000
Are you not afraid

11:40.520 --> 11:42.240
I might demand a blood debt from you?

11:44.600 --> 11:47.880
Your mother is watching us here.

11:48.480 --> 11:50.920
Why would I put you
in a difficult spot here

11:51.480 --> 11:53.080
and disturb her peace?

11:55.880 --> 11:57.200
After all these years,

11:58.240 --> 12:01.480
you have finally learned
to show care for your own sister.

12:03.560 --> 12:04.800
Seventeen years ago,

12:05.320 --> 12:07.920
when you recalled the troops
and rushed back to the capital,

12:08.000 --> 12:09.000
did you ever consider

12:10.800 --> 12:12.560
that your reckless decision

12:12.640 --> 12:15.440
would cost my father
and mother their lives?

12:19.920 --> 12:21.600
I will say it again.

12:22.520 --> 12:24.080
Seventeen years ago,

12:24.760 --> 12:28.280
I returned to the capital under
imperial command to suppress a rebellion.

12:28.360 --> 12:29.480
Is that so?

12:31.400 --> 12:34.960
Then dare you swear a bitter oath

12:35.800 --> 12:37.160
before my parents' tablets?

12:40.400 --> 12:42.800
Very well. Since we have come this far,

12:43.400 --> 12:44.280
let me

12:44.360 --> 12:47.000
have a frank word with you.

12:50.840 --> 12:52.360
I raised you

12:53.200 --> 12:57.320
for one reason only. To make you
the future of the Xie and Wei families.

12:57.840 --> 12:59.720
To bring honor to both our houses

13:00.560 --> 13:05.000
and guard the peace of Dayin.

13:05.600 --> 13:06.760
That is why

13:06.840 --> 13:08.640
I poured all my effort into raising you.

13:08.720 --> 13:10.040
Raising me?

13:11.400 --> 13:14.240
You merely forged a blade
fit for your hand.

13:15.720 --> 13:17.560
You just never expected

13:18.080 --> 13:19.360
that blade

13:20.160 --> 13:22.320
would one day turn against you.

13:24.720 --> 13:25.760
And you

13:26.920 --> 13:29.400
are the one who has disgraced our house

13:29.480 --> 13:31.360
and thrown the realm into turmoil.

13:34.320 --> 13:36.600
Bewitched by the daughter of your enemy,

13:36.680 --> 13:37.920
you forget loyalty and filial duty.

13:38.440 --> 13:41.280
And you dare speak to me
of loyalty to family and country?

13:41.800 --> 13:45.280
Today, before your parents,

13:45.360 --> 13:47.680
you will sever all ties with Fan Changyu.

13:47.760 --> 13:48.960
What right do you have

13:49.640 --> 13:51.240
to say such things to me here?

13:51.320 --> 13:53.040
I raised you for 17 years.

13:53.720 --> 13:55.040
Is that not enough?

13:58.320 --> 13:59.680
Do you acknowledge it

14:00.560 --> 14:01.920
or not?

14:05.760 --> 14:06.760
I acknowledge it.

14:10.520 --> 14:12.280
As your uncle,

14:13.440 --> 14:16.400
standing in place
of your father and mother,

14:16.480 --> 14:17.480
today,

14:18.000 --> 14:19.960
I will punish you by clan law.

14:20.560 --> 14:21.440
Tell him

14:21.960 --> 14:23.160
the sentence.

14:24.200 --> 14:25.400
According to clan rules,

14:25.480 --> 14:27.720
disloyalty and unfilial conduct
merit 108 lashes.

14:30.720 --> 14:31.800
Good.

14:33.760 --> 14:34.800
Every lash today,

14:35.400 --> 14:37.040
I will take willingly.

14:37.760 --> 14:39.240
Let this repay what I owe you.

14:42.120 --> 14:43.680
But from this day forward,

14:44.320 --> 14:46.280
never again speak of raising me

14:46.840 --> 14:49.360
or debts of gratitude.
Those words sicken me.

14:58.400 --> 14:59.240
Come!

15:13.040 --> 15:14.520
Our ancestors were upright,

15:15.040 --> 15:16.560
their names honored in history.

15:17.280 --> 15:19.000
Their teachings to sons and grandsons

15:19.960 --> 15:21.680
were always rooted in righteousness.

15:33.760 --> 15:34.880
BY IMPERIAL GRACE

15:47.600 --> 15:49.320
HONOR THE ANCESTORS, UNITE THE CLAN

15:49.400 --> 15:50.280
Thirty-five.

15:53.320 --> 15:54.200
Thirty-six.

15:57.520 --> 15:58.760
Thirty-seven.

16:00.160 --> 16:01.400
Thirty-eight.

16:03.160 --> 16:04.280
Thirty-nine.

16:06.400 --> 16:07.400
Forty.

16:08.040 --> 16:11.760
FAMILY PRECEPTS

16:13.080 --> 16:17.480
HONOR THE ANCESTORS, UNITE THE CLAN

16:25.560 --> 16:26.640
Ninety-nine.

16:44.120 --> 16:45.160
One hundred and four.

16:51.000 --> 16:52.040
One hundred and six.

16:54.720 --> 16:56.000
One hundred and seven.

16:59.520 --> 17:00.840
One hundred and eight.

18:11.240 --> 18:12.160
Yan Zheng.

18:15.680 --> 18:16.520
Yan Zheng.

18:31.440 --> 18:32.560
You should not have come.

18:33.920 --> 18:35.200
I know I shouldn't have.

18:36.360 --> 18:37.200
What about you?

18:39.600 --> 18:41.320
You knew Wei Yan would be here.

18:42.520 --> 18:44.080
Why come alone?

18:44.600 --> 18:46.120
Why submit to this punishment?

18:48.560 --> 18:51.360
General Fan, forcing your way
into the Xie family mausoleum

18:51.440 --> 18:53.320
is rather improper.

18:54.760 --> 18:56.240
I am not only General Fan.

18:58.320 --> 18:59.680
I am also the Marquis's wife.

19:00.320 --> 19:01.160
Why can't I be here?

19:01.240 --> 19:04.080
A proper marriage
requires a parents' consent

19:04.160 --> 19:05.600
and a matchmaker's word.

19:06.200 --> 19:07.200
And besides,

19:07.720 --> 19:09.880
where were the proper betrothal gifts?

19:11.360 --> 19:12.920
As for that so-called live-in marriage,

19:13.520 --> 19:15.440
even the name used was false.

19:15.520 --> 19:17.760
How could such a union be taken seriously?

19:17.840 --> 19:19.840
I have already taken the 108 lashes.

19:20.920 --> 19:23.880
You have no right to decide my affairs.

19:27.440 --> 19:29.640
A marriage letter is nothing but paper.

19:30.240 --> 19:31.640
If I acknowledge it,

19:32.920 --> 19:34.360
then it is real.

19:35.880 --> 19:37.800
-Let's go home.
-Wait.

19:44.640 --> 19:45.760
Join me.

19:49.360 --> 19:52.000
SPIRIT TABLET OF THE LATE LORD XIE LINSHAN
SPIRIT TABLET OF HIS WIFE, LADY WAN

20:02.880 --> 20:04.280
Father, Mother, please hear your son.

20:05.280 --> 20:08.120
Fan Changyu, a woman of Lin'an.

20:10.360 --> 20:12.200
She saved me…

20:14.960 --> 20:15.800
from death's door.

20:18.800 --> 20:20.760
When my heart had gone cold,

20:22.440 --> 20:23.960
she taught it to love again.

20:24.520 --> 20:26.800
I have spent more than ten years
on the battlefield.

20:28.640 --> 20:30.680
All that time, I never felt truly alive.

20:32.880 --> 20:33.920
Until I met her.

20:38.080 --> 20:39.960
Only then did I see life was worth living.

21:11.400 --> 21:13.400
Before your spirits above,
I make this vow.

21:14.200 --> 21:15.240
This woman

21:16.240 --> 21:17.520
is the companion of my life.

21:18.360 --> 21:19.720
I will never betray this vow.

21:21.120 --> 21:22.400
My heart will stay true till death.

21:48.760 --> 21:50.520
I will never betray this vow.

21:51.960 --> 21:53.680
My heart will stay true till death.

22:05.040 --> 22:06.280
My lord.

22:09.800 --> 22:10.640
Zheng.

22:12.600 --> 22:13.440
Zheng.

22:14.040 --> 22:14.920
Zheng.

22:16.520 --> 22:17.920
What happened to you?

22:18.000 --> 22:19.360
How did you get hurt this badly?

22:19.440 --> 22:20.680
I am fine, Aunt.

22:23.840 --> 22:25.320
This is Fan Changyu,

22:26.240 --> 22:27.080
my wife.

22:35.960 --> 22:36.920
Aunt.

22:37.520 --> 22:39.000
The Flower-Adorned General.

22:39.080 --> 22:41.160
I have long heard of your reputation.

22:43.400 --> 22:45.240
When my life hung by a thread,

22:46.440 --> 22:47.760
she saved me.

22:51.040 --> 22:51.880
We have

22:52.880 --> 22:54.200
pledged ourselves to one another.

22:55.080 --> 22:55.920
True till the end.

22:59.640 --> 23:00.560
Changyu,

23:01.080 --> 23:03.080
help Zheng inside and treat his wounds.

23:03.600 --> 23:04.760
Zheng, come.

23:26.800 --> 23:28.160
The night air is cold and heavy.

23:28.240 --> 23:30.360
Why have you come here, my lady?

23:31.040 --> 23:34.680
My lord, you forgot to bring
the osmanthus cakes you prepared.

23:34.760 --> 23:37.400
So I hurried over to deliver them.

23:39.800 --> 23:42.560
Zheng's mother used to love
osmanthus cakes.

23:43.520 --> 23:45.000
You miss her,

23:45.080 --> 23:47.320
so every year, you bring them for her.

23:48.040 --> 23:50.080
This year should be no different.

23:56.280 --> 23:57.120
It's for you.

24:06.960 --> 24:08.880
This box is beautifully crafted.

24:08.960 --> 24:11.800
Surely it came from a master artisan.

24:14.040 --> 24:16.040
Then I must eat more each day

24:16.640 --> 24:17.880
to make it worth

24:18.400 --> 24:20.680
the trouble you went through for me.

24:29.120 --> 24:31.520
Osmanthus cakes are very sweet.
Do not eat too many.

24:31.600 --> 24:32.440
I hear you.

24:55.600 --> 24:57.240
They suit each other so well.

24:57.320 --> 25:01.120
Even if Zheng's parents
are gone from this world,

25:01.720 --> 25:03.680
they would surely be pleased.

25:13.920 --> 25:15.600
-Fifteen, 20, ten!
-Fifteen, 20, ten!

25:16.400 --> 25:17.880
-Fifteen, 20, 20!
-Fifteen, 20, ten!

25:18.480 --> 25:19.320
Drink.

25:20.640 --> 25:23.000
What kind of nonsense game
is this from your hometown?

25:23.080 --> 25:24.360
I have lost all night long.

25:27.240 --> 25:28.280
Again.

25:28.360 --> 25:29.240
-Fifteen, 20,
-Fifteen, 20,

25:29.320 --> 25:30.520
-20!
-ten!

25:30.600 --> 25:32.200
-Fifteen, 20, ten!
-Fifteen, 20, ten!

25:32.960 --> 25:34.080
Drink.

25:36.080 --> 25:37.000
Come on.

25:38.000 --> 25:38.880
Master.

25:40.640 --> 25:41.920
What is it? Speak.

25:42.000 --> 25:43.240
There are no outsiders here.

25:44.680 --> 25:45.840
A letter has arrived for you.

25:52.600 --> 25:55.720
I knew Xie Zheng would never
give up searching for the truth.

25:57.600 --> 26:00.000
All that talk about uncle
and nephew was nonsense.

26:02.880 --> 26:04.400
It seems the time has come.

26:08.040 --> 26:09.120
Come with me.

26:10.040 --> 26:11.960
What is it? It is so late.

26:13.800 --> 26:16.800
I prepared a surprise for you.

26:24.360 --> 26:26.040
A ceremonial robe for you.

26:27.400 --> 26:28.320
What do you think?

26:49.520 --> 26:50.840
Have you lost your mind?

26:51.640 --> 26:53.560
That is the Empress's headdress!

26:54.960 --> 26:56.280
Become my Empress.

26:56.880 --> 26:58.520
Rule the realm beside me.

26:58.600 --> 27:00.080
Stand shoulder to shoulder with me

27:00.600 --> 27:02.040
and govern the empire.

27:07.360 --> 27:08.840
And if I were Empress?

27:09.840 --> 27:11.600
All you want is someone at your side,

27:12.320 --> 27:14.640
so that when your dream shatters,
you will not be alone.

27:18.240 --> 27:19.160
What is it?

27:20.800 --> 27:21.720
You do not like it?

27:23.400 --> 27:24.680
At this point,

27:25.200 --> 27:26.640
whether I like it or not

27:26.720 --> 27:27.880
makes no difference.

27:30.000 --> 27:31.360
You told me not to kill,

27:31.880 --> 27:32.880
so I stopped.

27:33.600 --> 27:34.760
And I have promised you

27:35.400 --> 27:37.000
I will not harm that child again.

27:38.320 --> 27:39.720
What more must I do

27:40.800 --> 27:42.720
before you agree to be my Empress?

28:04.600 --> 28:05.880
Kneel before me.

28:06.400 --> 28:07.640
Beg me.

28:13.560 --> 28:15.240
You expect me to kneel to you?

28:18.280 --> 28:20.720
I am the Emperor of this realm.

28:23.360 --> 28:24.440
What is it?

28:25.200 --> 28:26.280
You do not want to?

28:55.960 --> 28:56.920
I beg you.

28:57.960 --> 28:59.640
Be my Empress.

29:10.320 --> 29:12.680
Then I will wait for the day
I become Empress.

29:15.920 --> 29:17.280
That day will come soon.

30:12.120 --> 30:13.960
TIGER TALLY

30:24.680 --> 30:25.680
Stop playing around.

30:26.840 --> 30:28.160
Give me back the tiger tally.

30:56.840 --> 31:00.240
XIE RESIDENCE

31:07.680 --> 31:08.520
Marquis.

31:11.680 --> 31:12.560
Marquis.

31:13.760 --> 31:15.120
Madam, what happened to him?

31:15.200 --> 31:16.800
Take him to his room. Keep it quiet.

31:16.880 --> 31:17.720
Yes.

31:27.080 --> 31:29.960
Madam, perhaps you should rest.

31:30.040 --> 31:31.760
I can look after the Marquis.

31:31.840 --> 31:33.200
I will stay.

31:33.280 --> 31:34.640
All of you may leave.

31:35.400 --> 31:37.160
Unless something urgent happens,
do not come in.

31:37.760 --> 31:38.640
Yes.

31:54.040 --> 31:55.360
Changyu.

31:58.680 --> 32:01.200
After taking those 108 lashes…

32:03.600 --> 32:05.800
I can finally marry you properly,

32:07.640 --> 32:10.720
with matchmakers and the full rites.

32:26.840 --> 32:28.960
So you had already decided

32:30.320 --> 32:32.520
to atone this way.

32:35.720 --> 32:36.920
Changyu.

32:38.840 --> 32:40.680
Marry me,

32:42.920 --> 32:44.200
will you?

33:02.480 --> 33:03.720
We don't need to do it again.

33:04.880 --> 33:07.280
You belong to me. Always have.

33:43.800 --> 33:44.760
Mother…

33:46.520 --> 33:47.720
No…

33:48.880 --> 33:49.720
Mother…

33:51.880 --> 33:53.160
Let me die.

34:25.159 --> 34:28.000
This will cover your food and clothing
for the rest of your life.

34:28.520 --> 34:29.719
Take this bundle.

34:29.800 --> 34:31.920
Deliver it safely
to the General's residence.

34:32.000 --> 34:33.360
After that, leave the capital.

34:33.440 --> 34:35.000
Go as far away as you can.
Never come back.

34:37.239 --> 34:39.080
Madam, are you not coming with me?

34:41.440 --> 34:43.080
His eyes are everywhere.

34:43.600 --> 34:44.760
I cannot get away.

34:45.400 --> 34:46.480
If I leave,

34:47.000 --> 34:48.400
more people will die.

34:53.000 --> 34:54.159
Go now.

35:03.440 --> 35:04.400
Go.

35:59.320 --> 36:00.320
You are awake.

36:03.400 --> 36:04.440
Careful.

36:11.480 --> 36:12.720
Thank you

36:13.920 --> 36:15.240
for staying with me all night.

36:20.120 --> 36:22.320
You took so many lashes because of me.

36:23.920 --> 36:25.520
How could I leave you alone?

36:29.320 --> 36:30.760
For years,

36:31.360 --> 36:32.960
I thought Wei Yan despised me

36:33.560 --> 36:35.440
because when I was little,

36:35.520 --> 36:37.080
I went outside for osmanthus cakes,

36:37.160 --> 36:39.800
and it gave my mother
the chance to hang herself.

36:41.040 --> 36:43.720
I blamed myself all these years.

36:45.200 --> 36:48.600
But later, whether I retook Jinzhou
to avenge them

36:50.160 --> 36:51.520
or became Marquis Wu'an,

36:52.600 --> 36:54.160
the only thing that returned in my dreams

36:54.680 --> 36:56.960
was that sickening scent of osmanthus

36:57.800 --> 37:00.960
and the hem of my mother's dress
hanging from the beam.

37:05.680 --> 37:08.880
I was still that crying child.

37:10.320 --> 37:11.840
I never changed.

37:20.040 --> 37:21.480
But now you have me.

37:23.320 --> 37:24.680
I will protect you.

37:31.920 --> 37:32.840
Do you know,

37:33.360 --> 37:36.040
when you came out of Lin'an
covered in wounds

37:36.120 --> 37:38.160
just to find me,

37:38.880 --> 37:40.720
I thought to myself,

37:40.800 --> 37:42.880
what revenge?

37:42.960 --> 37:43.960
Forget it.

37:45.640 --> 37:47.120
I could not bear to see you cry.

37:49.800 --> 37:50.880
But then,

37:51.400 --> 37:53.520
I remembered I am a Xie.

37:55.800 --> 37:57.520
My father was Xie Linshan.

37:58.400 --> 38:00.600
I cannot even remember
what he looked like.

38:03.120 --> 38:04.760
But I still remember how his body

38:06.320 --> 38:07.880
was cut open and his chest

38:08.600 --> 38:10.800
was crudely stitched together
with needle and thread.

38:11.640 --> 38:13.520
And I remember the 67 arrow-shaped wounds

38:13.600 --> 38:15.360
across his body.

38:17.480 --> 38:18.440
Yan Zheng.

38:20.480 --> 38:22.120
I have never blamed you.

38:23.560 --> 38:25.400
Wei Yan is your uncle.

38:25.960 --> 38:27.600
He raised you for 17 years.

38:28.840 --> 38:30.800
Now the debt is repaid.

38:31.320 --> 38:32.480
The vengeance must be taken.

38:33.080 --> 38:35.040
Do not punish yourself

38:35.840 --> 38:37.320
for others' sins.

38:50.320 --> 38:51.320
All right.

38:54.240 --> 38:55.680
The time has come.

38:56.720 --> 38:58.360
At the palace banquet in three days,

38:58.440 --> 38:59.760
I will enter the palace myself

39:00.560 --> 39:02.840
and bring the palace maid witness
out with me.

39:03.720 --> 39:04.640
I will help you.

39:08.720 --> 39:09.760
Come in.

39:12.480 --> 39:13.840
Marquis. Madam.

39:14.680 --> 39:16.880
The falcon brought back
a chess record from the palace.

39:16.960 --> 39:18.480
Mr. Gongsun deciphered it.

39:18.560 --> 39:19.960
He sent this for you, Marquis.

39:27.920 --> 39:29.120
What is it?

39:32.840 --> 39:34.680
Wei Yan had an affair
with an imperial consort.

39:37.880 --> 39:40.120
LEARNING AND INTEGRITY

39:49.920 --> 39:52.560
This woman is the companion of my life.

39:53.640 --> 39:55.000
I will never betray this vow.

39:55.560 --> 39:56.880
My heart will stay true till death.

39:58.400 --> 40:00.040
My dearest Yan,

40:00.120 --> 40:01.520
your letter has brightened my day.

40:03.320 --> 40:05.440
Since we parted,
my longing for you has only deepened.

40:05.960 --> 40:07.600
Whenever I sit to dress my hair,

40:07.680 --> 40:09.120
I wear the hairpin you liked best.

40:10.840 --> 40:12.400
The garden blooms, alive with butterflies,

40:12.480 --> 40:14.040
yet there is no one
to share the view with.

40:15.680 --> 40:17.920
The elders in my family
have approved the marriage.

40:18.880 --> 40:20.280
All auspicious signs have gathered.

40:20.360 --> 40:21.880
Both families rejoice.

40:21.960 --> 40:22.960
The wedding rites are ready,

40:23.040 --> 40:24.160
and so are the gifts.

40:24.240 --> 40:25.080
IMPERIAL CONSORT QI RONGYIN

40:25.160 --> 40:27.120
Everything is in place now,

40:27.640 --> 40:29.160
except for you.

40:30.600 --> 40:32.000
I will never betray this vow.

40:32.560 --> 40:33.920
My heart will stay true till death.

40:45.120 --> 40:46.680
To my Yan,

40:47.800 --> 40:49.360
when you read this, imagine me before you.

40:50.600 --> 40:52.200
An imperial decree arrived
without warning.

40:52.880 --> 40:54.320
I have been summoned into the palace.

40:55.440 --> 40:57.120
Bound by His Majesty's command,

40:57.680 --> 40:59.040
I have no choice.

41:00.080 --> 41:02.000
I still remember
the letters you once sent.

41:02.640 --> 41:04.200
Every tender word lingers in my heart,

41:04.720 --> 41:06.040
as though you were speaking

41:06.560 --> 41:08.000
beside my ear.

41:08.600 --> 41:10.520
I remember the day
you placed flowers in my hair.

41:11.720 --> 41:13.240
Their fragrance still lingers.

41:13.760 --> 41:15.240
It feels as though it happened yesterday.

41:16.520 --> 41:18.320
The greatest sorrow in this world

41:19.000 --> 41:21.560
is loving someone yet being unable
to remain together.

41:22.400 --> 41:24.640
From this day on,
I will be confined in a golden cage,

41:25.240 --> 41:28.120
while my heart wanders with the clouds.

41:29.600 --> 41:31.360
If ever you see wild geese flying south,

41:32.680 --> 41:34.800
know that my letters
travel with them to you.

41:36.000 --> 41:37.080
Rongyin,

41:37.800 --> 41:39.760
written in tears before departure.

41:42.480 --> 41:44.480
LI RESIDENCE

42:15.560 --> 42:16.520
Grandfather.

42:17.920 --> 42:18.800
Guards.

42:19.320 --> 42:21.840
Take my dear brother into custody.

42:25.800 --> 42:26.960
What is going on?

42:28.000 --> 42:29.160
After the palace banquet,

42:29.680 --> 42:31.480
you will understand.

42:40.600 --> 42:42.360
You were only pretending to be ill.

42:42.440 --> 42:43.680
Wenkan.

42:44.800 --> 42:48.000
Do you know where you lost?

42:48.880 --> 42:51.760
Those who achieve great things
must act decisively

42:51.840 --> 42:54.360
and never be swayed by emotion.

42:54.440 --> 42:56.040
With a temperament like yours,

42:56.120 --> 42:58.160
you were never meant for great ambition.

43:00.400 --> 43:01.760
I act for the country.

43:02.280 --> 43:03.640
You act for personal gain.

43:03.720 --> 43:06.200
I could never be like you,
pushing forward,

43:06.720 --> 43:07.960
no matter the cost.

43:08.040 --> 43:09.600
Foolish child.

43:10.120 --> 43:12.560
All these years of loyalty
from our family.

43:12.640 --> 43:13.840
What did we gain from it?

43:13.920 --> 43:15.400
What did it bring us?

43:15.920 --> 43:17.080
Now that we have come this far,

43:17.160 --> 43:19.160
there is no turning back.

43:19.760 --> 43:21.560
We must ensure Qi Min takes the throne.

43:22.920 --> 43:24.880
Even if he proves no benevolent ruler,

43:24.960 --> 43:28.400
once the bow is drawn,
the arrow cannot be recalled.

43:29.600 --> 43:30.560
Wenkan,

43:31.080 --> 43:33.880
our clan numbers in the thousands
across nine branches.

43:33.960 --> 43:36.080
If you continue unable
to tell friend from foe

43:36.160 --> 43:37.120
or insider from outsider,

43:37.200 --> 43:40.080
you will bring ruin upon the entire family

43:40.600 --> 43:43.760
and shake the very foundation of Dayin.

43:47.520 --> 43:50.320
Since ancient times, the victor is king
and the loser a criminal.

43:50.400 --> 43:51.600
Only when it concerns

43:51.680 --> 43:53.880
one's personal interests
will one risk life for the country.

43:54.400 --> 43:56.600
You have read too many books.

43:57.200 --> 43:59.120
They have made you naive.

44:00.840 --> 44:02.040
Without my command,

44:02.120 --> 44:03.680
he is not to leave the residence.

44:03.760 --> 44:04.920
Yes.

46:48.600 --> 46:52.120
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

46:52.200 --> 46:53.080
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
